item.title: CVE-2019-7476|2024-08-04T20:46:46.406Z -- sonicwall -- global%20management%20system%20%28gms%29
item.description: A vulnerability in SonicWall Global Management System (GMS), allow a remote user to gain access to the appliance using existing SSH key. This vulnerability affects GMS versions 9.1, 9.0, 8.7, 8.6, 8.4, 8.3 and earlier.
